<td align="center"><b>
<i>Nomada festiva</i> <font size="-1" face="sans-serif">Cresson, 1863</font></b><br>
<small><i>Nomada &#40;Heminomada&#41; festiva </i>Cresson, 1863</small><p>
<a href="/mp/20q?search=Life">Life</a>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/mp/20q?search=Insecta">Insecta</a>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/mp/20q?search=Hymenoptera">Hymenoptera</a>
